subject: Tennis
Rogers Cup (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: The Ukrainian qualifier Lesia Tsurenko, ranked 54th, upset No. 9 Garbiñe Muguruza, 7-5, 6-1, in the Rogers Cup in Toronto.
